  </div>

          
          
          <div class="QuoteTweet-text tweet-text u-dir" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="2" dir="ltr">Darn it.         <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">18-24 year olds voting intention:

LAB: 68%
CON: 16%
LDEM: 8%
GRN: 3%
UKIP: 1%

(via <a href="/ICMResearch" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="130827937"><s>@</s><b>ICMResearch</b></a>)<a href="https://t.co/TmyU29HQVr" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="http://hopenothate.org.uk/2017/06/03/young-people-think-election/" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="http://hopenothate.org.uk/2017/06/03/young-people-think-election/"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="js-display-url">hopenothate.org.uk/2017/06/03/you</span><span class="invisible">ng-people-think-election/</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>

<p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="3">Robin Moss added,</p>
  
      <div class="QuoteTweet&#10;    &#10;    &#10;    u-block js-tweet-details-fixer">
  <div class="QuoteTweet-container">

      <li class="embed-link js-actionEmbedTweet" data-nav="embed_tweet">

  </ul>
